### 关键决策
- **占用判定口径**：已支付 = `pending_shipment / pending_receipt / pending_use / pending_review / completed`（项目里没有 `paid` 枚举值，按下单流转后状态等价为已支付）+ 待支付 = `pending_payment` 且 `created_at > now() - 15min`
