- **新增** `backend/app/services/button_intent_resolver.py`：统一按钮意图解析器
  - `resolve_button_intent(intent, button_type, ai_function_type, capture_purpose)` 按 P1→P5 优先级翻译为 `report_interpret` / `drug_identify` / `None`
  - P1 显式 intent > P2 老顶层 button_type > P3 ai_function + 老子类型 > P4 ai_function + image_capture + capture_purpose > P5 兜底 None
